<plot>Nick, a sloppy kid who can't even tie his necktie right, is warned by his friend Don, a snappy dresser who is obviously bound for success, that he better wake up or he'll find himself a derelict, smoking cigarettes in a dirty hotel room. Don's words get Nick to thinking about his future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?542847</url></doc>
